title: Virgin Japanese Camellia Oil, Organic 100ml(3.52oz)
description: Camellia oil is derived from the seeds of camellias, a kind of evergreen shrub with shiny leaves and rose-like flowers. Camellia oil is known to be effective multi-purpose moisturiser. It has been used in parts of Asia by women to nourish both their skin and hair for centuries. It penetrates quickly and deeply, leaving the skin with optimum hydration and no greasy feel. It can help reduce fine lines, acne scarring, the appearance of pores and diminish pregnancy stretch marks or prevent them. It contains Vitamins A, B, C, E and Polyphenol, natural antioxidants that safeguard your skin from the damaging effects of UV/environmental exposure and free radicals. It offers similar benefits for hair. It adds shine, softness and smoothness to your hair. Packaged in glass bottle to protect the contents from heat, light, oxidation and moisture. Ingredients: Organic Japanese Camellia (Camellia japonica), Cold Pressed, Unrefined, Organic and Fair for Life Certified
